object.text: Cool music! Amazing stylish interior. Huge menu. Try steamed dorada, almond cake and melon and mint smoothy. My fav shisha is mint+grapefruit. You might spend all day long in this place.
Great coffee, a couple of tables and stable wifi
Nice business lunch and cosy atmosphere
Best tea I ever had! Excellent service, free internet (no password), good daytime events and so on! Island of silence and peace. (Oh, yes and it's a bookstore.)
Great Sirniki with Smetana and Jam , perfect breakfast , coffee here is delicious too
Borsh is good, pork is tasteless,cheese cake is good, price is greatly below market. Service is so so. Live music vary stiles badly. But the voice is good.  U may pay with your card.
